  <p class="fc-light-700 lh-relaxed mb4">
    The <code>.link--overlay</code> and <code>.link--wrapper</code> classes allow you to make an
    entire container clickable while keeping semantic HTML for SEO. Based on
    <a
      href="https://blog.enodo.io/fr/comment-integrer-correctement-un-lien-pour-le-seo-4.html"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
